{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/frontend/vue-cli-3-ie-polyfill/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"cereme.dev","author":"cereme","siteUrl":"https://cereme.dev","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"cereme/cereme.dev"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"86f920b0-97ba-541d-a800-23fcd7fc023c","excerpt":"Vue 앱을 IE에서 켜다보면 화면이 제대로 나오지 않거나, 빈 페이지가 나오거나 한다. Polyfill을 하면 해결된다.  main.js에 추가 vue.config.js에 webpack 설정 추가\n만약 없다면 루트 디렉토리에 파일을 만들면 된다.","html":"<p>Vue 앱을 IE에서 켜다보면 화면이 제대로 나오지 않거나, 빈 페이지가 나오거나 한다.</p>\n<p>Polyfill을 하면 해결된다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add babel-polyfill</code></li>\n<li>\n<p>main.js에 추가</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'babel-polyfill'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//add this line</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Vue <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'vue'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./plugins/vuetify'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> App <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.vue'</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>vue.config.js에 webpack 설정 추가\n만약 없다면 루트 디렉토리에 파일을 만들면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\nconfigureWebpack<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    entry<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"babel-polyfill\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./src/main.js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"Vue cli 3에서 IE11 Polyfill 하기","date":"May 09, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/frontend/vue-cli-3-ie-polyfill/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/backend/aws-lambda-cloudwatch-event-cronjob/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AWS Lambda와 Cloudwatch의 Event를 통해 주기적으로 Lambda 함수 실행하기","category":"backend","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/frontend/serve-vuejs-on-flask-setting/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Flask에서 Vue.js 템플릿 사용하기","category":"frontend","draft":false}}}}}